name: Warbarons - A classic turn based strategy game
blurb: Competitive turn based multi / singleplayer strategy game in your browser.  No download or plugins, free and a fun mature community.

rewards.reward: The great feeling of helping a indie project that needs all the help it can get.
Get listed with your name as an enthusiastic supporter under credits (digital and paper) + 2 month silver membership.
Pay a couple of terrain tiles for us and get listed under Warbarons contributor under credits +3 months gold membership. +Invent a name for an AI player or a city name.

6 months pre paid gold membership.
+your gold member icon will be in unique color identifying you as one of our funders.
+Get access to the latest versions before they are released to be able to test and give input on new features and balancing. 
+All previous rewards

When gold membership is available you have 1 year paid.
+ Get access to our game design forum section where we list all new features planed for the coming versions of warbarons.
+Get the printed manual in color / story about making the game.
+All previous awards

We will design a new item for the game with you. When we have enough reference material our artist will draw it. You get to give it a unique name which could include your own name.\r\n+ All previous awards

Gold account level forever.
New campaigns, extra heroes and other add-ons that we plan to release as upgrades are always available on your account at no fee.
